With a number output `{python} 6 * 7`.

With a string output `{python} 'a string'`.

With an array output `{python} [1, 2, 3]`.

With an object output `{python} dict(a=1,b=dict())`.

With no language specified and no output `{}a + b`.

With execution mode specified and no output `{javascript} c * d`.
